text: Hafidullah (born 1 March 1996) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his List A debut on 12 January 2017 for Federally Administered Tribal Areas in the 2016–17 Regional One Day Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Federally Administered Tribal Areas cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
